A vintage 1920s-style propaganda poster aesthetic depicting a powerful woman in a sharp formal coat standing at the front of a grand parliamentary hall, her silhouette commanding attention. Behind her, five other women in period-appropriate professional attire stand in a diagonal formation, each casting long dramatic shadows across marble floors. The color palette features muted sepia tones with bold crimson accents. Geometric Art Deco patterns frame the composition, with strong angular light streaming through tall arched windows. The women's expressions are determined and forward-looking, their poses conveying quiet authority and historical significance.
